Which store location had the highest sales this week?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest weekly sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'WTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this month?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest MTD sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'MTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this year?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT('The best selling product category is ', LC.CATEGORY_LABEL, ' with ', FORMAT(CAST(SUM([REVENUE_UNITS_TY]) AS BIGINT), '###,###,###,###,###'), ' units sold.') FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_SALES_ACCELERATOR] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_CATEGORY] LC ON SA.CATEGORY_CD = LC.CATEGORY_CD GROUP BY LC.CATEGORY_LABEL ORDER BY SUM([REVENUE_UNITS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this yesterday?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest sales yesterday of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'DAY' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest weekly sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'WTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this month?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest MTD sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'MTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this year?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest YTD sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'YTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this yesterday?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest sales yesterday of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'DAY' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which are the best-selling product categories?

FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_SALES_ACCELERATOR] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_CATEGORY] LC ON SA.CATEGORY_CD = LC.CATEGORY_CD GROUP BY LC.CATEGORY_LABEL ORDER BY SUM([REVENUE_UNITS_TY]) DESC;

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest weekly sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'WTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this month?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest MTD sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'MTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;

Which store location had the highest sales this yesterday?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest sales yesterday of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'DAY' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which are the best-selling product categories?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT('The best selling product category is ', LC.CATEGORY_LABEL, ' with ', FORMAT(CAST(SUM([REVENUE_UNITS_TY]) AS BIGINT), '###,###,###,###,###'), ' units sold.') FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_SALES_ACCELERATOR] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_CATEGORY] LC ON SA.CATEGORY_CD = LC.CATEGORY_CD GROUP BY LC.CATEGORY_LABEL ORDER BY SUM([REVENUE_UNITS_TY]) DESC;

Which store location had the highest sales this week?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest sales yesterday of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'DAY' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this month?

Which store location had the highest sales this week?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest weekly sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'WTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this month?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest MTD sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'MTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this year?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest YTD sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'YTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this yesterday?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest sales yesterday of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'DAY' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which are the best-selling product categories?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT('The best selling product category is ', LC.CATEGORY_LABEL, ' with ', FORMAT(CAST(SUM([REVENUE_UNITS_TY]) AS BIGINT), '###,###,###,###,###'), ' units sold.') FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_SALES_ACCELERATOR] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_CATEGORY] LC ON SA.CATEGORY_CD = LC.CATEGORY_CD GROUP BY LC.CATEGORY_LABEL ORDER BY SUM([REVENUE_UNITS_TY]) DESC;

Which store location had the highest sales this week?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest weekly sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'WTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this month?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest MTD sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'MTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this year?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest YTD sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'YTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this yesterday?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest sales yesterday of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'DAY' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;

FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_SALES_ACCELERATOR] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_CATEGORY] LC ON SA.CATEGORY_CD = LC.CATEGORY_CD GROUP BY LC.CATEGORY_LABEL ORDER BY SUM([REVENUE_UNITS_TY]) DESC;

Which store location had the highest sales this week?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest weekly sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'WTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this month?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest MTD sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'MTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this year?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest YTD sales of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'YTD' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which store location had the highest sales this yesterday?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT(LL.LOCATION_LABEL, ' is the location with the highest sales yesterday of ', FORMAT(SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]), 'C')) FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_RETAIL_SALES_ANALYSIS] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_LOCATION] LL ON SA.LOCATION_CD = LL.LOCATION_CD WHERE TIMEFRAME = 'DAY' GROUP BY LL.LOCATION_LABEL ORDER BY SUM(SA.[REVENUE_DOLLARS_TY]) DESC;
Which are the best-selling product categories?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT('The best selling product category is ', LC.CATEGORY_LABEL, ' with ', FORMAT(CAST(SUM([REVENUE_UNITS_TY]) AS BIGINT), '###,###,###,###,###'), ' units sold.') FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_SALES_ACCELERATOR] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_CATEGORY] LC ON SA.CATEGORY_CD = LC.CATEGORY_CD GROUP BY LC.CATEGORY_LABEL ORDER BY SUM([REVENUE_UNITS_TY]) DESC;
Which are the best-selling product categories?

SELECT TOP 1 CONCAT('The best selling product category is ', LC.CATEGORY_LABEL, ' with ', FORMAT(CAST(SUM([REVENUE_UNITS_TY]) AS BIGINT), '###,###,###,###,###'), ' units sold.') FROM [DASHBOARD].[STORY_SALES_ACCELERATOR] SA JOIN [STORY].[LKP_CATEGORY] LC ON SA.CATEGORY_CD = LC.CATEGORY_CD GROUP BY LC.CATEGORY_LABEL ORDER BY SUM([REVENUE_UNITS_TY]) DESC;
